p93
aVPerhaps they were looking for a subliminal effect.
p94
aVStrike three.
p95
aVNow, I wasn\u2019t having a very good time to start with, so perhaps the political messages stood out more with me than your average moviegover.
p96
aVI found \u201cKingsman: The Secret Service\u201d to be derivative, loud and overly broad.
p97
aVJackson\u2019s lisping billionaire was fun for a while, but then started to get on my nerves.
p98
