aV\u201cJurassic Park\u201d was first released on June 11, 1993.
p408
aVAnd, it has held up over the years, a true classic.
p409
aVIt ranks as the 20th highest-grossing film in North America.
p410
aVIt\u2019s about $85 million short of hitting the one-billion dollar mark.
p411
aVI doubt if this latest theatrical release will bring that much money.
p412
aVBut, there will be plenty of folks willing to visit \u201cJurassic Park\u201d just one more time for some really cool 3D enhanced effects.
p413
