p415
aVThe 3D effects seem more pronounced than at the theater.
p416
aVThe brim of Bob Peck\u2019s hat came right out of my television (seemingly).
p417
aVOf course, the day scenes were better than the night scenes.
p418
aVAt night, some of the 3D effects were harder to spot and enjoy.
p419
aVBut, overall, JP3D was a first rate home theater experience.
p420
aVHighly recommended.
