p1098
aV\u000a\u000a\u000aWith his \u201cgolden age\u201d seeming like a bygone era \u2013 Billy Madison, Happy Gilmore, I even like The Waterboy \u2013 and his brief-but-bold dramatic turns feeling more like cliff notes in his career \u2013 Punch Drunk Love, Spanglish \u2013 I want to be able to like Adam Sandler again.
