aVJust a throwaway piece of dialogue from Christopher McQuarrie's otherwise quotable Oscar-winning screenplay for The Usual Suspects.
p1298
aVWatch Bryan Singer's awesome neo-noir a second time and you might find that this seemingly extraneous information gives a big clue to the real identity of arch criminal Keyser Soze.
