aV\u000aKingsley Amis thought Cameron's science fiction sequel "a flawless masterpiece" (he and son Martin once fell out over the subject) but that would be going too far.
p2431
aVIt is, however, a slick, satisfying and deeply influential movie which keeps its chase-plot going with furious momentum.
