aVWith the dialogue-free first act of WALL-E, Pixar challenged the assumptions underlying family animated movies.
p2639
aVThe little robot's courtship of EVE had the physical aplomb of a silent movie, each character constructed out of the minimum of elements required to make us love them.
p2640
