p2641
aVWith Up, Pixar and Disney continue their adventure in pared-back storytelling, repudiating the pernicious received wisdom that what children require from a film is the discharge from a blunderbuss of pop culture gags, demographically-engineered characters, infantile wisecracks and celebrity voices.
