aV\u000aYou have to take your big pointy hat off to director Peter Jackson (Brain Dead, Heavenly Creatures).
p3296
aVHis adaptation of fantasy's founding trilogy is unprecedentedly ambitious.
p3297
aVShooting all three epic films back to back was fraught with logistical nightmares (all those extras and special effects shots, a punishing 274-day shooting schedule) and commercially audacious, defying the will of original backers Miramax, who would have preferred a self-contained blockbuster.
p3298
aVHis The Fellowship Of The Ring opens with a brisk primer of Middle-earth history, loading the exposition up front.
p3299
aVRings were issued to the leaders of the various peoples of this fantasy land, yet one was created that could control them all - an evil Ring worn by the dark lord Sauron.
p3300
